-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Every year Scott Robertson, a generally admired Yale student, and his
screw-up mate C.J. Longhammer from Minnesota cross the Wisconsin border
for a wild night. Scott has a girl in his Saab, but as usual must return
to the bar as CJ started a fight and this time Scotts adoring kid brother

Scotts fists get them out. They are followed by a black Cadillac, make a
risky drive on the lake to shake it, allow Robbie to take an urgent leak

in Arctic weather. The Cadillac keeps following and even ramming them,
so they start wondering why and suspecting each-other, and it gets worse..
